subject: World Cup (Soccer)
World Cup 2014 (Soccer)
Soccer
lead_paragraph: In African World Cup qualifying, Egypt beat Zimbabwe, 2-1, in Alexandria, rewarding around 10,000 fans allowed in to watch an Egyptian home game for the first time in more than a year.
